								<col width="100">
								<col width="50">
								<col />
								<col width="100">
								<col width="100">
								<col width="150">
								<!-- 序号：1 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="6">1</td>
									<td rowspan="6">外观与结构</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">牙机/治疗机的外表面应光滑、平整，不允许有凹凸、碰伤和粗糙不平的缺陷。</td>
									<td rowspan="6">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f600]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f600']) && $produce['report']['f600'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f600']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f600]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f600']) && $produce['report']['f600'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 									
									</td>
									<td rowspan="6"> 
										<input type="radio" name="data[f601]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f601']) && $produce['report']['f601'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f601']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f601]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f601']) && $produce['report']['f601'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 										
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">油漆件/喷涂件表面应光洁，无露底、脱落、起泡、发黏及影响外观的修补痕迹。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">患者或操作者可触及的部件和零件的边和角应不会伤害患者或操作者。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">连接到牙机上的器械管子应是可拆卸的，以便于清洁和消毒。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">各种文字符号应清晰、准确、牢固。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">牙椅的头枕、扶手、靠背、座垫和脚垫应使患者轻松地坐或卧，并且操作者可以在符合人机学最佳位置上进行操作。</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：2 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="4">2</td>
									<td rowspan="4">运动部件</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">在正常工作情况下，可能造成损害的运动部件，应加以防护或覆盖。</td>
									<td rowspan="4">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f602]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f602']) && $produce['report']['f602'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f602']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f602]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f602']) && $produce['report']['f602'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 	
									</td>
									<td rowspan="4">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f603]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f603']) && $produce['report']['f603'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f603']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f603]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f603']) && $produce['report']['f603'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">电动部件应提供限位开关以限制其动作范围，并对限位开关的失效提供附加保护装置。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">所有管道和电缆应适当防护，以免在正常使用时，由于摩擦、弯曲或拉伸导致的磨损、断裂和损坏。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">牙机/治疗机装配应牢靠，紧固件应牢固，活动部件应灵活可靠。</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：3 -->
								<tr>
									<td>3</td>
									<td>噪音</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">牙机的转动部分运转应平稳，无不正常的杂声。整机噪声应不大于70 dB(A)。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">dB(A)</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f604]" value="{$produce['report']['f604']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
									<td>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f605]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f605']) && $produce['report']['f605'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f605']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f605]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f605']) && $produce['report']['f605'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：4 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="5">4</td>
									<td rowspan="5">操作控制装置</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">控制装置的位置排列应在避免意外触发的位置。</td>
									<td rowspan="5">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f606]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f606']) && $produce['report']['f606'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f606']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f606]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f606']) && $produce['report']['f606'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 	
									</td>
									<td rowspan="5">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f607]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f607']) && $produce['report']['f607'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f607']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f607]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f607']) && $produce['report']['f607'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}>  
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">各操作件指示应正确，动作应可靠。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">操作符号应符合YY/T 0628 的规定。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">当牙科手机正常放置时，控制装置应能防止其意外启动。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">当牙科手机工作时，控制装置应能防止牙科病人椅的意外启动。</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：5 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="2">5</td>
									<td rowspan="2">供水与供气</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">水、气路管道应有明显的颜色区分。</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f608]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f608']) && $produce['report']['f608'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f608']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f608]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f608']) && $produce['report']['f608'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 	
									</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f609]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f609']) && $produce['report']['f609'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f609']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f609]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f609']) && $produce['report']['f609'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">水、气路系统应畅通，各阀应操作方便，启闭灵活。</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：6 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="2">6</td>
									<td rowspan="2">地箱</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">在地箱的自来水输入水连接处应安装一个过滤器，以防止自来水供应系统的微粒进入到牙机内的水系统。</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f610]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f610']) && $produce['report']['f610'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f610']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f610]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f610']) && $produce['report']['f610'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 	
									</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f611]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f611']) && $produce['report']['f611'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f611']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f611]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f611']) && $produce['report']['f611'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">在地箱的输入气连接处应安装一个过滤器，以防止空气压缩机供气系统的微粒进入到牙机内的气系统。</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：7 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="6">7</td>
									<td rowspan="6">冲盂漱口<br />给水装置</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">痰盂清洗水出水口和溢出水位之间的空气间隙的距离应不少于20 mm。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">mm</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f612]" value="{$produce['report']['f612']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
									<td rowspan="6">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f613]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f613']) && $produce['report']['f613'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f613']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f613]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f613']) && $produce['report']['f613'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">水压为200 kPa时，痰盂清洗水水流应达盂底整周。</td>
									<td rowspan="3">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f614]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f614']) && $produce['report']['f614'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f614']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f614]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f614']) && $produce['report']['f614'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 	
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4"  class="t_aling_l">痰盂清洗水水流应不会溅出痰盂。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4"  class="t_aling_l">漱口给水装置的出水应柔直，无飘溅现象。</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">痰盂下水道通畅，下水速率应不少于4L/min。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">L/min</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f615]" value="{$produce['report']['f615']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">痰盂下水口内应配有固体收集器，能截留直径 ≥2 mm的任何固体废物。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">mm</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f616]" value="{$produce['report']['f616']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：8 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="2">8</td>
									<td rowspan="2">三用喷枪</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">密封性应良好，启闭灵活，喷出物应均匀，喷射方向应能调节。</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f617]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f617']) && $produce['report']['f617'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f617']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f617]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f617']) && $produce['report']['f617'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 	
									</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f618]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f618']) && $produce['report']['f618'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f618']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f618]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f618']) && $produce['report']['f618'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">分别按动水路或气路按钮时，水、气应分清，两个按钮同时按下时，喷出物应成雾状。</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：9 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="2">9</td>
									<td rowspan="2">热水器</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">热水器应使用安全特低电压（SELV）进行操作。</td>
									<td >
										<input type="radio" name="data[f619]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f619']) && $produce['report']['f619'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f619']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f619]" value="不符合" title="不符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f619']) && $produce['report']['f619'] == '不符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
									<td rowspan="2">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f620]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f620']) && $produce['report']['f620'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f620']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f620]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f620']) && $produce['report']['f620'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">恒温性能应稳定，漱口水和热水三用喷枪水的温度应为40 ℃±5 ℃。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">℃&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f621]" value="{$produce['report']['f621']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：10 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="4">10</td>
									<td rowspan="2">吸唾器<br />弱吸唾器</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">水压为200 kPa时，真空度应不少于15 kPa。</td>
									<td >
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">kPa</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f622]" value="{$produce['report']['f622']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
									<td rowspan="4">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f623]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f623']) && $produce['report']['f623'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f623']))}checked{/if}>
										<input type="radio" name="data[f623]" value="返工后符合" title="返工后符合" {if isset($produce['report']['f623']) && $produce['report']['f623'] == '返工后符合'}checked{/if}> 
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">水压为200 kPa时，抽水速率应不少于400 mL/min。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">mL/min</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f624]" value="{$produce['report']['f624']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="2">吸唾器<br />强吸唾器</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">气压为500 kPa时，真空度应不少于25 kPa。</td>
									<td >
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">kPa</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f625]" value="{$produce['report']['f625']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">气压为500kPa时，抽水速率应不少于1000 mL/min。</td>
									<td>
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">mL/min</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f626]" value="{$produce['report']['f626']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
								</tr>
								<!-- 序号：11 -->
								<tr>
									<td rowspan="5">11</td>
									<td rowspan="5">器械盘</td>
									<td colspan="4" class="t_aling_l">在各个工作位置都应稳定，盘面偏斜度应不大于3°。</td>
									<td >
										<span style="float: right; line-height: 25px;" class="font_s8">°&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
										<input style="width:50%" type="text" name="data[f627]" value="{$produce['report']['f627']|default='/'}" lay-verify="required" placeholder="" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input input_no_bro session1_1 height25" onfocus="if (value =='/'){value =''}" onblur="if (value ==''){value='/'}">
									</td>
									<td rowspan="5">
										<input type="radio" name="data[f628]" value="符合" title="符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;合" {if (isset($produce['report']['f628']) && $produce['report']['f628'] == '符合') || (!isset($produce['report']['f628']))}checked{/if}>
